16:
Lord Whitetail! I am humbled and
grateful to be in your presence...
19:
Say, Claw... Don't you think this is a
bit... messed up?
23:
Huh? Whaddya mean? I DID have to
improvise in a few places, but it
should be no biggie! Just think
about it:
27:
The original festival is about a
celebrated old guy giving out
presents, yeah? People respect you,
so I figured you'd be the best person
to do the gifting.
31:
Uh-huh. Well, it's depressing.
God dammit. This must be why Alk
insisted I take that stuff with me.
45:
What are you DOING, bro? You can't
just go and put on your strange
reindeer Santa outfit! People are
gonna freak out!
48:
Can it. This is a hundred times better
than the weird gloomy ceremony
you came up with!
51:
All right, everyone, drink up! Eat up!
And no more bowing and groveling.
It's weird.
53:
This place has the vibe of a funeral.
Let's get those energy levels up and
have ourselves a celebration!
58:
I-in that case, I will have some of
this food, Lord Whitetail.
61:
I told you, I ain't no lord! And I'm not
Whitetail—
69:
Um, bro... Did you already pour
yourself a strong one before this, or
what? Your nose is all red.
73:
I can imagine it would be difficult to
do something like this sober.
77:
*sigh* I just wanted to add on to the
Legend of Whitetail, you know? Write
a new, grand chapter—something
to go down in history!
80:
Frankly, I'm surprised at you,
Claudius. You should have known
Lord Nimbus was never going to
behave in a stiff ceremony like this.
85: Yeah, not sure what I was thinking.
92:
Oh man, this party is really getting
wild. So much for the reverent,
respectful event I envisioned!
95:
Pfft, reverence, shmeverence... Spare
me the formal crap!
99:
Bro... Are you sure you haven't had a
bit much to drink? I really don't want
Light to go off on me again...
104:
Excuse me, could we please try
some of this food?
106:
Huh? Yeah, sure, take whatever you
like.
108:
Thanks.
By the way, Mister, are you actually
Whitetail?
112:
I'm no "mister", and I'm sure as hell
not Whitetail. I'm SANTA, kid! You got
that?
115:
More like a weird
Santa/reindeer/tiger hybrid, but
okay.
120:
Y-you idiot! You can't say something
like that! Isn't he like some sort of
catfolk royalty?!
121:
Yeah, but like... I can't keep up with
people who party that hard, you
know?
125:
Damn, kids these days are cheeky.
Were you like that when you were a
cub, Claw? I feel like you were.
129:
Uh, no way! I was a way more
charming, loveable, and all-around
adorable kid! Heh.
132:
High praise for yourself, eh. Might I
suggest adding "humble" to that list?
136:
Hard to believe that their people
were at war not too long ago...
140:
It's amazing. Everything you guys
did... is freaking amazing!
145:
Oh boy. You know Nimbus has had a
few too many drinks when he starts
complimenting other people!
148:
Shut up! Come on, at least let me
say that much.
158:
Why exactly are you wearing that
preposterous outfit?
164: So? What is it you want from me?
167:
Nothing, really. Just came by to see
if you were still causin' trouble for
Claw, that's all.
169:
And what exactly could I possibly
do, in my current state? You took
everything away from me!
172:
All right. If you haven't been doing
anything, I suppose that's all I have
to say. Sorry to waste your time.
183:
Listen here, imposter who dares to
wear the name Whitetail. I have a
favor to ask of you. You said you
were on a journey, yes?
184:
If you were to ever come across Lord
Selenius on your travels... Please
give him this.
188:
That I greatly regret I could not be
by his side.
195:
I'll let him know.
I promise.
